Package model

Class Division

java.lang.Object
model.Division
public class Division extends Object
This is the Division(FLD for short) class. This class holds the methods for building FLD objects and getting and setting FLD attributes.

      public Division(int divisionID, String divisionName, LocalDate createDate, LocalTime createTime, String createdBy, Timestamp lastUpdate, String lastUpdateBy, int countryID)

      Parameters:
      divisionID - The first level division's ID.
      divisionName - The division's name.
      createDate - The division's create date.
      createTime - The division's create time.
      createdBy - The person who created the division data.
      lastUpdate - The division's last update time.
      lastUpdateBy - The person who last updated the division data.
      countryID - The country ID the FLD belongs to.
